OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776115935
OL,3,CThree charged in terror probe after
OL,4,Calleged damage at firm's premises
OL,6,FA police officer from Hampshire and
OL,7,FIsle of Wight Constabulary was
OL,8,Fassaulted, but was uninjured, and
OL,9,Fthree people were arrested, Counter
OL,10,FTerrorism Policing South East (CTPSE)
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FCTPSE said it had taken the lead for
OL,14,Fthe investigation "due to the
OL,15,Fcircumstances of the incident".
