OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776115935
OL,3,CThree charged in terror probe after
OL,4,Calleged damage at firm's premises
OL,6,FSteven Davies, 57, of Slade Road,
OL,7,FBirmingham, Dolores Gnapi, 34, of
OL,8,FTariff Crescent, Lewisham, south-east
OL,9,FLondon, and Ian Roberts, 51, of
OL,10,FMcDougall Road, Wednesbury, West
OL,11,FMidlands, have been charged with
OL,12,Faggravated burglary and criminal
OL,13,Fdamage.
OL,15,FRoberts was also charged with
OL,16,Fassaulting an emergency worker.
OL,18,FThey were remanded in custody to
OL,19,Fappear at Westminster Magistrates'
OL,20,FCourt on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
